title: 2020 Bingo Card
description: Leah and Melissa are joined by special guest Chase Strangio for a big recap episode of a big week. They cover some developments on the orders list and two major decisions (the Title VII decision and the DACA decision).
author: hey@crooked.com (Crooked Media)
